sql:
SELECT AVG(attempts) AS avg_rushing_attempts
FROM rushing_statistics
WHERE stat_id = 2;

external_knowledge:
The passing and rushing statistics are assumed to be calculated per game; Average passing/rushing statistics = (Sum of passing/rushing statistics) / (Number of games); 
Winning and losing statistics are calculated separately to compare the performance of each team in wins and losses; 
The conference and division of each team are included to provide context for the team's performance.
